Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.32,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}BON-BON Cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.89,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.48,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}RAN-RAN Welcome party
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.09,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look up! Sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:51.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:54.16,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The presence... of asteroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:55.76,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As they confoundedly collide and melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.54,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sing loudly! Like a Sirenger
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.70,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:03.15,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be the one with the last laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:10.05,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because I'm wearing a sailor uniform {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}And that's that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.31,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though it's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.80,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm feeling horrible. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:22.85,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The summer clothes are so much better! {\fnaquafont\fs34.5}←{\rs}Oh, so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.96,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's getting close to 3 picts. Yet, I'm still hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:30.00,ls_op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Try your best! Get your spirits up! My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:02.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:03.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.05,0:01:31.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.60,0:01:35.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.14,0:01:38.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The year just flew by, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:39.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have another good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:40.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Course...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:44.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll be bidding farewell to some\Nof you guys in three more months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:46.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess who I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:46.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:48.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean me, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.16,0:01:49.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can believe, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:54.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People always talk about the New Year's mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:56.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I guess there's kind of a weird atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:59.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it changes the second school starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:01.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:05.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that New Years wields a mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:09.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite the fact that I spent the first three\Ndays of the year busy working at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:11.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I gained weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}New Year's magic, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The cold weather makes it difficult to burn off your fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did a lot of moving around, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days of busy work as a shrine maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you ate just as much, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:22.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. New Year's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:23.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. Zoni soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:24.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Snacks! Snacks! Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.28,0:02:25.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden. Snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But the pictures of having fun during New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:31.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...usually include badminton...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:32.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and kite flying...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:37.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've never actually seen someone do those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:38.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:42.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These days, it's dangerous with stuff like electric lines and cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:44.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just watched TV and read books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:46.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After those first three busy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:47.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I did those.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed badminton, One Hundred\NPoets, and Pin the Tail on the Donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:54.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't match your image.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.35,0:02:57.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My family follows western customs...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:59.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but our relatives in the country are more traditional.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We wore kimonos and went to the temple on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:05.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I had fun with my cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An omnipotent god...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:10.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Way more Japanese than I am!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More traditional than my family!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, why Pin the Tail on the Donkey?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In One Hundred Poets...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.67,0:03:16.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're all 31 syllable poems, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:17.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You read out the first verse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and look for the card with the rest of the poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:22.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:23.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:25.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a beginner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:28.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The experts snatch up the cards in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:30.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:33.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand playing a game that\Nmakes you feel like you're studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People like you who view mental games as a\Nchore are why Japan's going down the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:41.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why couldn't they use One Hundred Poets for like a card battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:42.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could summon a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Think there was a Semimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Semimaru uses a shining attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ono no Komachi uses a lovely strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that sound fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:50.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to your world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:55.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But wouldn't more physical\Ngames have helped you lose weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was those stupid rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice cakes are loaded with calories, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One as big as a matchbox...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is equivalent to a whole bowl of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:08.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that Kagami's eating a bowl of rice with each bite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:08.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You also ate rice cakes, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:14.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom's gone, so I've rarely had zoni soup and that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't really eat rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:18.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:21.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,With zoni soup, sweet red bean soup, soy flour rice cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many fun ways to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:27.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's gonna lose to the rice cakes again next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:27.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:32.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to eat for New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:34.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...instead of rice cakes, Izumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like pizza and pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:39.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Our year starts with raw pasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:43.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad cleans out the pasta machine at the end of every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:44.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That thing rusts if you don't use it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use it without cleaning it first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the pasta ends up all black and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we clean it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and make pasta and pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:58.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds very thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kagami's house probably orders\Npizza, and their pasta consists of cup noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More like...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have pizza or pasta on New Year's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:07.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:10.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't go with traditional foods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:10.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes great with roast chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:14.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a traditional New Year's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:17.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Under western traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:22.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you have for New Year's, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:23.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:27.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family sounds all wealthy and western...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you probably didn't have traditional stuff or rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you had like a full course French dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.00,0:05:34.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:37.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate traditional foods...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I was unable to bite through a rice cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it stretched like whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:44.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with this walking pillar of moe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rice cake goes whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:49.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But New Year's goes by so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:50.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:52.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter break goes by fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be a long vacation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but after cleaning, writing\NNew Year's cards, and homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you don't have much time to relax, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:00.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do New Year's cards this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.08,0:06:03.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you copied my homework yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:07.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have your first dream of the year, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it supposed to be a good\Nomen if you dream about certain things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:16.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, it's one: Mt. Fuji, two: hawk, three: eggplant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:18.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Officially, you would add...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:22.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...four: fan, five: tobacco, six: blind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes all the way up to six!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.27,0:06:25.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ever dreams about that kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:29.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dream would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why a blind man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:31.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:32.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:35.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to dream about all of those at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of those showed up in your dreams,\Nyou'd be really blessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:40.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I believe that just one will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:45.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would have to dream about\Na hawk twice and an eggplant three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:47.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And quite frankly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.15,0:06:50.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Who really remembers what they dream about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:53.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People who care about that stuff are\Nhaving way too much fun with New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:54.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In my first dream this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:07:00.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I opened my shoe locker to find my shoes missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I had no choice but to take\Nshoes from someone else's open locker...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the size was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:10.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up the meaning of this dream in\Nthe encyclopedia for dream fortune telling...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it said that it's a sign I am\Npursuing skills useful to society...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:18.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it will take a while before I accomplish that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The shoes apparently represent societal standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheesecake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...pretty ambitious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:28.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I kinda understand, but kinda not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:36.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Another person was goofing off on the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...during the coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:41.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they realize they're representing Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:44.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes you wonder why they even bother going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:49.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't want to go to a boring coming-of-age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And this girl's gonna grow up to be a bad person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:56.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys going to wear to your ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:59.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well go with a long-sleeve kimono...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:05.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's probably going to have\Nme wear a long-sleeve kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:06.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see him doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.25,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:08.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you wear one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:12.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'd look more like a little kid going to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.00,0:08:13.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:14.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope ya had fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, Cousin Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my husband was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And a lot happens during New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:24.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and my sister had a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a weak body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:26.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:29.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It definitely wasn't because I didn't\Ngive her any New Year's allowance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:34.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only a cop would reveal what she was\Nreally thinking before I've said a thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:36.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A One Hundred Poets tournament is currently underway...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it's been one crazy ride so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:44.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do on New Year's when you were a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:45.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.82,0:08:48.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I did all kinds of stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:49.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:55.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:56.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:56.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:57.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:58.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She really just goes with the flow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never heard her say anything serious.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:05.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I outgrew my memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:14.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's always cooped up under the kotatsu these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:17.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.07,0:09:18.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotatsus are so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to the bathroom's a pain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you shouldn't say that so loudly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:28.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have a surefire way to get a person out of a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:29.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay under the kotatsu too long...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:34.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll get stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So your dad doesn't need a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He likes them as much as anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we've both fallen asleep\Ntogether under the kotatsu before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:47.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But they say that you'll catch a\Ncold if you fall asleep under a kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:48.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we turn it off once someone notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a mix of heaven and hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:57.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like right before you turn it on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and after you turn it off, it feels even colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:06.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And doesn't it really suck when you get out of bed in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at it, it's totally freezing after you\Nget undressed and before you get in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But not enough to make you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You might slip and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:18.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And doesn't it suck when you need to go\Nthe bathroom in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:19.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:20.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:21.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:25.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the walk from the bus to the classroom is also hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It always gets a lot more exciting this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, it's awkward how everyone tries to act normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:36.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you can still feel the tension in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:39.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone special on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and confessing your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and having them reciprocated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:43.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just see it as a conspiracy by the chocolate industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:54.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you could say it's also a special time of year for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:57.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a sale on the unsold chocolate afterwards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I go after the chocolate power to make my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:02.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, you have no dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Money can't buy love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, that's what they like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:08.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but isn't Valentine chocolate a\Nway of showing love through money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:12.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess someone who's only\Nexperienced love in games has some harsh views.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:17.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in games, it's all about upping\Nyour relationship level before the day comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:22.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't do anything special for Valentine's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys dream too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:26.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody managed to trigger the Kagami flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:31.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:32.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about flags and relationship levels...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I seriously get worried about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't limit yourself to events in games.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:44.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand those narrow-minded people\Nwho don't know what they're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, events only take a few hours in game time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so Valentine's Day is usually over in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:53.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:57.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But this year, I'm planning on giving chocolate to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:01.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone playing the same online game as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend from your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving it to him in person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.23,0:12:08.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not actually going to meet the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be in-game.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the characters are still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that even count?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:18.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just meant a game character.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.29,0:12:20.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you insult my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're married in-game, and my character's male.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:25.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:28.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So the guy is giving the girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:31.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And wouldn't it be like a girl giving a girl chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:32.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If the other person's a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:33.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:35.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other person's a guy in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:41.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it doesn't matter as long as you're having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.65,0:12:48.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yesterday, Miyuki-san was like...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:54.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Females giving chocolates on February 14th is a Japanese custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.59,0:12:52.87,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In western society, people of both genders...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...give chocolate and cards to friends and people they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.41,0:13:02.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:05.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so a girl like me could still get lots of chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could interpret it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you sure have a lot of confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you already know for a fact that you'll be popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In foreign countries, little girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:14.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No risqué statements allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.18,0:13:18.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:18.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you accept this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:20.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Valentine's Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:24.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible wrapping...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:25.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...for a uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the inside's all cool and heart-shaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:30.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I put some effort into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:33.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's always enthusiastic about this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was making them until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's only friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:38.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't give any friendship chocolate to guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:42.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll definitely get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:43.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami's giving me chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.34,0:13:49.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa was making hers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I just joined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:51.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:59.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you always look skilled, but secretly work behind the scenes is so moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.74,0:13:59.50,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:03.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:08.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:10.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, it's a just friends thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry the shape's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The shape isn't important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is that you made it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time's the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:33.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you give anybody chocolate, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave chocolate to my father and a relative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:40.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave chocolate to everybody I'm friendly with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave chocolate to you, Tsukasa, and Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:43.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure had a boring St. Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need to hear it from someone who lives in an online game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:50.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cousin was accepted to Ryouou, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.44,0:14:54.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:56.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty far from her home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so she'll be living with us starting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:00.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been like a little sister anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we've been in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:02.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:04.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But next to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:06.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...nobody would be able to tell who's younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's like a little sister in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's that small?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she got accepted to our school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...your cousin must be really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That just sounds like you're being really presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:18.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a student here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I barely passed the exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exams, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be taking our exams next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:28.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll be spending the whole year studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:30.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I even take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even picked a major.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously need to start thinking about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:40.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Studying, manual labor, and me just don't mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:43.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of future do you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}I design games. 'Cause it's my hobby.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:49.36,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Megas smoked cheese-nyoro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.61,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}There can only be one truth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.53,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}And this isn't it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use a hobby to make profit and make games...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be a self-proclaimed manga artist who can only sell at Comiket...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or perhaps, indulge your curiosity\Nand become a professional writer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.55,0:15:56.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, maybe just a novelist who aims for a niche market.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:59.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since you like computers, I guess art design might work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:03.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe a scenario writer who uses\Nrandom material instead of an actual story writer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or she doesn't go to college...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:06.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or they're all the same thing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:07.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:12.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.11,0:16:22.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She shook us off last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:22.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1150,685.5)}Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:23.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(234,688.5)}Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:23.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(484,688.5)}Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:31.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We will absolutely make sure she\Nreaches the goal known as our register!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:32.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be at a loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then allow us to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...help her find her way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:40.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let 'er rip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:41.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:42.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:42.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:43.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:43.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:44.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:45.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:48.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:52.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Attempting to determine Legendary Girl A's objective for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:52.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:53.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Countin' on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:55.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the newest comic out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:55.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:57.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Volume 14 of Sgt. Frog, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:57.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:16:59.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the height of our goods to the appropriate level...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:01.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring them to the attention of Legendary Girl A!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.09,0:17:01.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And deploy the flyers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.06,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Deployment complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:06.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:09.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on her movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And as Legendary Girl A approaches the register...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...deploy our best-selling goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:16.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:19.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:24.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl A's objective isn't the comics section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:25.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:29.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch target to the DVD section.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:30.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:35.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...block all side paths so Legendary Girl A...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:36.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...heads straight to the new DVD section!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:37.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:40.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama! Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Gero-gero-gero build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.83,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Tama-tama-tama build-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:03.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...picked up the item!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:06.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally become a winner today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:07.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us have a wild celebration tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:10.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:14.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a feint!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to bring out my trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:29.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:34.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring that bargain, super-rare, out-of-print DVD to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:37.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She is heading for the register.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The crowd inside me is cheering with applause right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:47.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:48.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:51.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your total comes to 1,785 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:03.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm short 3 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:06.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:09.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please put that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:23.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.97,0:19:25.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick this into gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:29.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on the thirteenth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:30.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know, I'm your navigator, Akira Kogami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:34.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:37.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.09,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Minoru Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:39.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.28,0:19:40.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.13,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.28,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on episode 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:43.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Into the second season.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.97,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.80,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.79,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:49.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we've reached the fifth station on Mt. Fuji, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:52.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can drive up to the fifth station.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:56.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've climbed Mt. Takao before!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:00.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have something else to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.28,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}D-D-D-D-D-D-D-D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:06.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama's twin drills look wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wonderful about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The way they go round and round like a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:13.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:14.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a special announcement today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The results for the Lucky Star figure poll!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have Akira-sama announce the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The characters that will soon be getting figures are Konata Izumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.99,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama, do a proper job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, everybody knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.39,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:37.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just means that the higher-ups think the\Nactual show is more important than this corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:42.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.61,0:20:44.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The producers agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.40,0:20:45.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:47.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just fall for your little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:49.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already used to being backstabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:50.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Little trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.85,0:20:52.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an awful thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:57.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't tell me that it says you're going to have a figure made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:20:59.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:02.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be making a figure of Konata Izumi-san this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:05.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the popular Minoru Shiraishi will also get a figure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:06.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:16.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please send us any suggestions or\Ncomments you have about the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:19.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave them on our home page.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:21.65,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:25.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:26.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.77,0:21:27.40,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:28.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All the staff members can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:29.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Drill!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.89,0:23:03.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Sgt. Frog:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:03.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:05.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean next time on Lucky Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:06.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gero-gero.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:09.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade, I have a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:11.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese anime is now a global industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If we use it to brainwash the people on Pekopon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.57,0:23:16.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can complete the invasion of Pekopon in no time, sah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:18.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a genius, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:20.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:22.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A soldier should act like a soldier and use brute force!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:23.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth, you red dharma doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:28.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In this age, whoever controls information controls the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, your prehistoric mind wouldn't understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:32.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You better watch yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:33.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:34.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Under One Roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:36.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.85,0:23:37.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gero!
